{"article_id":"2xQuaUT5VnjfKEM5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The admission is in ;","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"the sentence awaits us .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Army Sergeant Bowe Bergdahl admitted","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"deserting his Afghan post","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and endangering fellow troops .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"By all accounts this is the most serious betrayal of presidential authority in my life time .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"In 2014 President Obama attempted to cover Bergdahl with the achievement of a war hero ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"even inviting his Idaho based parents to the Rose Garden","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"to celebrate news of his release .","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"President Obama pointed out at the time","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"that five Taliban leaders were freed from Guantanamo","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"so that Bergdahl could be released from captivity .","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"To gild the lily ,","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"National Security Adviser , Susan Rice , said","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"Bergdahl served \" the United States with honor and distinction . \"","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"Yet everyone in the White House and the Pentagon knew","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"this was a lie with monumental implications .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"In fact , Army officials refused to list Bergdahl as a POW .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"An internal 2009 Army report found","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"that he walked off his post on more than one occasion","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and even said","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"he wanted to join the ranks of the enemy .","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"This report also noted","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"he shipped his laptop back to Idaho with a note","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"expressing his disillusionment with the American position in the war .","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"President Obama had all of this information at his disposal","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"before he made a deal","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"releasing Bergdahl .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Why then did he mislead the American people ?","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"The answer can be found in the president ' s desire","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to satisfy antiwar liberals","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"keen on emptying Gitmo .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"At the Rose Garden event the president admitted as much","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"when he said ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"\" We ' re committed to winding down the war in Afghanistan","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"and closing Gitmo. \"","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"It is instructive that the CIA has evidence","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"at least three of the released Taliban leaders have returned to the battlefield .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"One intelligence official argued :","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"\" It ' s probably a tie as to who is the bigger traitor \" - Bergdahl or Obama .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"With this exchange and the elevation of Bergdahl ' s rank , the president compromised national security knowingly and willfully .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"Although Bergdahl will not receive capital punishment","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"when his sentence is determined ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"he probably should be tried as a traitor","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"whose actions led directly to three soldiers","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"seriously injured during search and rescue missions","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"to find him .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"if this fiasco is linked to American injuries and , perhaps deaths ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"one might well ask","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"if the commander in chief should be held accountable as well .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"The president ' s dissimulation clearly violated the military code","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"and has had a profound effect on morale .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Those","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"I know in the military","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"invariably ask","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"how a president could honor a deserter","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"when he was fully aware of his prior actions .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"This , of course , wasn ' t the first time","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"President Obama allowed politics to determine a course of ethical behavior ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"but it may be among the most egregious examples .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"One intelligence official argued :","depth":3},{"id":62,"text":"\" It ' s probably a tie as to who is the bigger traitor \"","depth":4},{"id":63,"text":"- Bergdahl or Obama .","depth":4},{"id":64,"text":"With a political ecology","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"in which standards have been debased ,","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"many have attempted to rationalize President Obama ' s decision .","depth":3},{"id":67,"text":"In my judgment , however , his actions","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"that jeopardized national security","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"should be fully investigated","depth":4},{"id":70,"text":"and ,","depth":4},{"id":71,"text":"where blame exists ,","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"the full weight of public opinion should be employed","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"to condemn the president and his assistants .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":147,"left":137,"right":146,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":137,"left":134,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":113,"right":133,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":79,"right":112,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":75,"right":78,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":5,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":2,"right":7